posting_body: ['Look-and-Lease Special: Now offering up to $1000 off your first full month of rent if you apply within 48 hours of touring our community!', 'Welcome to Solara', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 14', 'OR Text', '14', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 499 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Discover your new home at Solara Luxury Apartments in Seattle, WA.', 'Here you will find a living experience that blends city with serene balance.', 'Our pet-friendly apartments are located in North Seattle and offer modern one, two, and three-bedroom homes.', 'Our homes also come equipped with cozy amenities such as private patios, walk-in closets, and more.', 'We’re focused on our residents’ wants and needs and it shows in our luxurious community and apartment amenities.', 'We strive to provide a welcoming atmosphere with all the perks and amenities that will make you feel at home.', 'Call us to apply and schedule a tour today!', 'Features:', 'Dishwashers, Stainless Steel Appliances, Expansive Windows, Private Patios, Quartz Countertops, Large Walk-In Closets, In-Unit Laundry', 'Community Amenities:', 'Expansive Fitness Center, Resident Court Yard, Business Center and Internet Lounge, Puppy Play Area & Dog Wash, Barbeque, Club Lounge, Game Room, Theatre Room', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats - allowed', 'Dogs - allowed', 'Comments: Breed restrictions apply.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Must make 3X the monthly rent to qualify', 'Need more information?', 'Copy this link:', '<URL>', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'QxVN7GHB354']
